    "experiment": "unconstrained_oblique_baselines",
    "description": "Accuracy and direction diversity for unconstrained oblique tree baselines. Methods: ManualSPORF (matched), ManualSPORF (full), ObliqueFIGS, FIGS axis-aligned. Each example is one fold with predict_* fields for each method's metric score.",
